#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:3
msgid ""
"The AI Assistant is a streaming chat interface embedded in the Gereedschap "
"tab of the caseworker dashboard. It connects a configurable LLM to a "
"registry of data sources via the [Model Context Protocol]{1} (MCP), allowing "
"caseworkers to query process definitions, running instances, tasks, "
"decisions, deployments, legislation, knowledge graph data, and deployed "
"process bundles in natural language."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:5
msgid ""
"Sources and models are selected per session. See [LLM Provider Architecture]"
"{1} for how providers and models are registered and extended."
msgstr ""

