#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:150
msgid "`mcpChat.service.ts`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:152
msgid ""
"`runChatStream(history, userMessage, emit, selectedProviderIds, modelId, "
"signal?)` is the agentic loop entry point. It resolves the correct "
"`LlmProvider` from `LlmRegistry` by `modelId` and the scoped tool "
"definitions and system prompt from `McpRegistry` by `selectedProviderIds`. "
"The service has no direct dependency on any LLM SDK."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:154
msgid ""
"Text deltas arrive via the `onDelta` callback supplied to "
"`LlmProvider.streamTurn()` and are emitted immediately, so the user sees "
"tokens in real time. See [LLM Provider Architecture — Response delivery]{1} "
"for the streaming vs. buffered trade-off."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:156
msgid ""
"**Tool result truncation.** Each tool result is capped at 12,000 characters "
"before being added to the messages array. Multi-round queries against "
"Operaton list endpoints can return large JSON payloads; without truncation "
"the accumulated messages array exceeds the 200,000-token API limit."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:158
msgid ""
"**AbortSignal threading.** The signal is passed to `client.messages.stream()"
"` and checked before each tool execution. This ensures a timed-out or "
"disconnected request does not leave an orphaned Anthropic API call running."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:159
msgid ""
"// The event types emitted by runChatStream\n"
"export type ChatStreamEvent =\n"
"  | { type: 'status'; message: string }\n"
"  | { type: 'delta'; text: string }\n"
"  | { type: 'done' }\n"
"  | { type: 'error'; message: string };\n"
"\n"
"export type ChatEventCallback = (event: ChatStreamEvent) => void;"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:170
msgid "`mcp.routes.ts`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:172
msgid ""
"`POST /v1/mcp/chat` flushes SSE headers immediately after the pre-flight "
"guards pass, then drives `runChatStream` and writes events to the response."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:173
msgid ""
"res.setHeader('Content-Type', 'text/event-stream');\n"
"res.setHeader('Cache-Control', 'no-cache');\n"
"res.setHeader('Connection', 'keep-alive');\n"
"res.setHeader('X-Accel-Buffering', 'no'); // disables Caddy / nginx proxy "
"buffering\n"
"res.flushHeaders();"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:181
msgid ""
"A single `AbortController` covers both the 480-second hard timeout and "
"client-disconnect cleanup (`req.on('close', ...)`). A `send()` helper guards "
"`res.writableEnded` before each write so a disconnecting client cannot cause "
"a write-after-end error."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cmcp-ai-assistant.md:183
msgid ""
"**Audit log exclusion.** `POST /v1/mcp/chat` is excluded from "
"`audit.middleware.ts` alongside `GET /v1/admin/audit`. Chat turns are high-"
"frequency and do not require an audit trail."
msgstr ""

